@startuml seq-live-refresh
'' PlantUML over Mermaid because this is THE flagship round trip across six processes/modules whose message
'' ORDER, async hops, and activation lifetimes are the whole story; PlantUML sequence gives autonumber,
'' activation bars, == phase == dividers and per-participant concept colour that Mermaid cannot colour.
'' Colour macros in _vv-theme.iuml expand only in skinparam/<<#…>>; participant colours are the literal
'' palette hexes (slate #3A5BA0 main, amber #B1951D IPC, teal #2D9574 renderer, blue #4F97D7 re-frame,
'' green #67B11D markdown, purple #A45BAD DataScript).
!include _vv-theme.iuml

title Live refresh — editor save -> painted DOM (one full round trip)\nINVARIANT: content cache changes; UI/navigation state is untouched

autonumber "<b>[0]"

actor "User /\neditor" as ED FS_TINT
participant "chokidar\nwatcher" as CK FS_TINT
participant "main service\n(Node)" as SVC MAIN_TINT
participant "preload\nwindow.vv" as PL IPC_TINT
participant "renderer.core\n bridge!" as BR RENDERER_TINT
participant "re-frame\nevents/fx" as RF REFRAME_TINT
participant "unified\nremark/rehype" as MD MARKDOWN_TINT
database "DataScript\nconn" as DS DATASCRIPT_TINT
participant "views\nmarkdown-body" as V RENDERER_TINT

== detect (filesystem) ==
ED -> ED : save README.md
CK -> CK : awaitWriteFinish\n(stabilityThreshold 80ms)
CK -[#9F8766]-> SVC : "change" event (path)
activate SVC
SVC -> SVC : kind-of path → "markdown"\nfs.readFileSync utf8
SVC -[#B1951D]-> PL : webContents.send\n**vv:content** {:path :kind "markdown" :text}
deactivate SVC
activate PL
PL -[#B1951D]-> BR : ipcRenderer.on("vv:content")\n→ window.vv.onContent(cb)
deactivate PL
activate BR
BR -> RF : rf/dispatch\n**[:content/received {…}]**
deactivate BR

== transact (DataScript content cache) ==
activate RF
RF -> RF : handler (PURE): build base via cond->\n(omit :doc/text if nil; retract stale :doc/error)
RF -> DS : fx **:ds/transact**\n{:doc/path :doc/kind :doc/text :doc/stamp}
activate DS
DS -[#B1951D]-> RF : tx-report → [:ds/changed]\n(:ds/rev inc)  — subs :tabs/:doc/active recompute
deactivate DS

== render (Markdown, async) ==
RF -> MD : fx **:markdown/render** {:text :path :on-done}
deactivate RF
activate MD
MD -> MD : unified()\ncollect {:html :toc :assets}
MD -->> RF : Promise<result> .then\n-> rf/dispatch **[:content/rendered path stamp result]**
deactivate MD
activate RF
RF -> DS : fx :ds/transact\n{:doc/html :doc/toc :doc/assets}
activate DS
DS -[#B1951D]-> RF : [:ds/changed] → :ds/rev inc
deactivate DS
deactivate RF

== paint (DOM, no VDOM diff) ==
DS --> V : :doc/active sub recomputes (new :doc/html)
activate V
V -> V : component-did-update →\n**set! (.-innerHTML node) html**
note right of V #FFF6D6
  Only the .markdown-body innerHTML changes.
  :ui/find ranges, scroll position, active theme,
  and history are in app-db — NOT touched by any
  :ds/* transaction, so they survive the refresh.
end note
deactivate V

legend right
  |= Colour |= Participant / concept |
  |<#9F8766>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;| filesystem / editor / chokidar |
  |<#3A5BA0>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;| main process (Node IO service) |
  |<#B1951D>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;| IPC seam (preload, contextBridge) — all amber arrows |
  |<#2D9574>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;| renderer / reagent view |
  |<#4F97D7>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;| re-frame events + effects |
  |<#67B11D>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;| Markdown (unified/remark/rehype) |
  |<#A45BAD>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;| DataScript content cache |
endlegend
@enduml
